# Ghostty resources downloaded by setup.sh from the thdxg/ghostty release,
# mirroring a real Ghostty.app layout (ghostty/{themes,shell-integration} plus a
# sibling terminfo/). Macterm ships them verbatim; nothing here is committed, so
# the whole directory is ignored. (No trailing slash so it also matches a
# symlink at this path, as dev worktrees may use.)
